command: add contact/customer name and phone number in the table
sql:
SELECT
    j.jobno,
    j.vregno,
    j.description,
    j.dated,
    j.status,
    j.amount,
    c.name AS customer_name,
    c.telephoneno AS customer_phone
FROM
    jobs AS j
INNER JOIN
    contacts AS c ON j.customerid = c.customerid
WHERE
    j.status = 'Pending';

command: Show table of all pending jobs
sql:
SELECT *
FROM jobs
WHERE status = 'Pending'; -- Filter jobs based on the 'status' column to show only 'Pending' jobs.

command: Show me a table of all the pending jobs
sql:
SELECT *
FROM jobs
WHERE status = 'Pending';
-- This query selects all columns from the 'jobs' table where the 'status' is 'Pending'.
